  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    EU Settlement Scheme: ID document scanner locations
  </h1>
</div>

  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Locations where you can go to get your biometric ID document scanned if you do not have an Android device with near field communication (NFC).
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

